---
// La relación con tu cliente: promesa + mockup de la pantalla de aprobación
// (lo que ve el cliente de la agencia al abrir el link).
// White-label: el cliente nunca ve "Manny"; el encabezado es de la agencia.
---

<section class="benefit">
  <div class="section-wrap benefit-grid">
    <div class="benefit-copy">
      <h2 class="display-h2 benefit-h2">
        El feedback de tus clientes,
        <span class="italic-accent">todo en un mismo lugar.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="lead benefit-lead">
        Le pasás el calendario o las piezas con un link. Mira, comenta y
        aprueba en cualquier momento, desde cualquier lugar.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mockup"
      role="img"
      aria-label="Pantalla de aprobación que ve el cliente: piezas del mes con botones para aprobar o comentar"
    >
      <div class="mockup-head">
        <span class="mockup-brand">Estudio Norte</span>
        <span class="mockup-meta">Tu contenido de julio</span>
      </div>

      <ul class="piece-list">
        <li class="piece">
          <span class="piece-thumb"></span>
          <span class="piece-main">
            <span class="piece-name">Post · jueves 9</span>
            <span class="piece-note">La cosecha llega al salón</span>
          </span>
          <span class="piece-chip" data-state="ok">Aprobada</span>
        </li>
        <li class="piece">
          <span class="piece-thumb"></span>
          <span class="piece-main">
            <span class="piece-name">Reel · sábado 11</span>
            <span class="piece-note">Detrás del mostrador</span>
          </span>
          <span class="piece-chip" data-state="ok">Aprobada</span>
        </li>
        <li class="piece">
          <span class="piece-thumb"></span>
          <span class="piece-main">
            <span class="piece-name">Story · lunes 13</span>
            <span class="piece-note">Anuncio de horarios</span>
          </span>
          <span class="piece-actions">
            <span class="piece-btn piece-btn-primary">Aprobar</span>
            <span class="piece-btn">Comentar</span>
          </span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="comment">
        <span class="comment-author">Valeria (cliente)</span>
        <span class="comment-text">¿Va con el logo nuevo? Si es así, aprobado.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .benefit {
    padding-block: var(--space-16);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .benefit {
      padding-block: var(--space-24);
    }
  }

  .benefit-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-12);
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .benefit-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-20);
    }
  }

  .benefit-h2 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6);
  }

  .benefit-lead {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 560px;
    color: var(--neutral-800);
  }

  /* --- Mockup: pantalla de aprobación ---------------------------------- */

  .mockup {
    background-color: var(--background);
    border: 1px solid var(--neutral-300);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .mockup-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
  }

  .mockup-brand {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .mockup-meta {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--neutral-600);
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .piece-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .piece {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6);
  }

  .piece + .piece {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
  }

  .piece-thumb {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: var(--neutral-200);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .piece-main {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .piece-name {
    font-size: var(--text-body-small);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--foreground);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .piece-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--neutral-600);
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }

  .piece-chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .piece-chip[data-state='ok'] {
    color: #059669;
    border: 1px solid rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.35);
  }

  .piece-actions {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-left: auto;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .piece-btn {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--neutral-300);
    color: var(--neutral-800);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .piece-btn-primary {
    background-color: var(--foreground);
    border-color: var(--foreground);
    color: var(--background);
  }

  .comment {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
    margin: 0 var(--space-6) var(--space-5);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    background-color: var(--neutral-200);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border-top-left-radius: 2px;
  }

  .comment-author {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--neutral-600);
  }

  .comment-text {
    font-size: var(--text-body-small);
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  @media (max-width: 479px) {
    .piece-note {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
